to start a Kerberos 5 authentication server
at boot time.
.It Va kadmind5_server_enable
.Pq Vt bool
Set to
.Dq YES
to start
.Xr k5admind 8 ,
the Kerberos 5 Administration Daemon; set to
.Dq NO
on a slave server.
.It Va rwhod_enable
.Pq Vt bool
If set to
.Dq YES ,
run the
.Xr rwhod 8
daemon at boot time.
.It Va rwhod_flags
.Pq Vt str
If
.Va rwhod_enable
is set to
