.Pa /etc/motd
will not be updated
.It Va nfs_client_enable
.Pq Vt bool
If set to
.Dq YES ,
run the NFS client daemons at boot time.
.It Va nfs_client_flags
.Pq Vt str
If
.Va nfs_client_enable
is set to
.Dq YES ,
these are the flags to pass to the
